WEBVTT

00:04:59.490 --> 00:05:02.172
AG: Joshua Foer is a science journalist.

00:05:02.196 --> 00:05:05.616
For as long as he could remember,
he'd had a terrible memory.

00:05:05.640 --> 00:05:09.577
What are the things that you've always had
the hardest time remembering?

00:05:10.077 --> 00:05:13.152
JF: (Laughs) Let's see.

00:05:13.176 --> 00:05:15.424
Like, why I just opened the refrigerator.

00:05:16.950 --> 00:05:19.085
To put the toilet seat back down.

00:05:19.109 --> 00:05:24.702
Just about every important anniversary
and birthday of family members.

00:05:25.044 --> 00:05:27.099
(Laughs)

00:05:27.123 --> 00:05:30.337
I think maybe I've forgotten
some of the things that I've forgotten.